!! Monokai Pro Theme

This theme implements the beautiful Monokai Pro color scheme with both dark and light variants.

!! CSS for Monokai Pro Dark Theme

```css
/* Monokai Pro Dark Theme */
.tc-theme-pmu-monokai-dark {
    --monokai-bg: #2d2a2e;
    --monokai-fg: #fce566;
    --monokai-comment: #5c5955;
    --monokai-string: #a8ff60;
    --monokai-number: #ff73fd;
    --monokai-keyword: #ff6188;
    --monokai-function: #fd971f;
    --monokai-class: #a6e22e;
    --monokai-operator: #f92672;
    --monokai-variable: #f8f8f2;
    --monokai-selection: #49483e;
    --monokai-border: #75715e;
}

.tc-theme-pmu-monokai-dark .tc-tiddler-frame {
    background-color: var(--monokai-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--monokai-border);
}

.tc-theme-pmu-monokai-dark .tc-tiddler-title {
    color: var(--monokai-class);
    font-weight: bold;
}

.tc-theme-pmu-monokai-dark h1, .tc-theme-pmu-monokai-dark h2, .tc-theme-pmu-monokai-dark h3 {
    color: var(--monokai-class);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--monokai-border);
}

.tc-theme-pmu-monokai-dark code {
    background-color: var(--monokai-selection);
    color: var(--monokai-function);
    border: 1px solid var(--monokai-border);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 2px 4px;
}

.tc-theme-pmu-monokai-dark pre {
    background-color: var(--monokai-selection);
    border: 1px solid var(--monokai-border);
    border-radius: 5px;
    padding: 10px;
}

.tc-theme-pmu-monokai-dark .tc-tag-list {
    background-color: var(--monokai-selection);
    border: 1px solid var(--monokai-border);
}

.tc-theme-pmu-monokai-dark .tc-tag {
    background-color: var(--monokai-keyword);
    color: var(--monokai-bg);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 2px 6px;
    margin: 2px;
}

.tc-theme-pmu-monokai-dark a {
    color: var(--monokai-string);
    text-decoration: none;
}

.tc-theme-pmu-monokai-dark a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
}

.tc-theme-pmu-monokai-dark .tc-sidebar {
    background-color: var(--monokai-selection);
    border-right: 1px solid var(--monokai-border);
}

.tc-theme-pmu-monokai-dark .tc-tiddler-controls {
    background-color: var(--monokai-selection);
    border: 1px solid var(--monokai-border);
}

/* Apply dark theme to body */
body.tc-theme-pmu-monokai-dark {
    background-color: var(--monokai-bg);
    color: var(--monokai-fg);
}

/* Apply dark theme to main content areas */
.tc-theme-pmu-monokai-dark .tc-story-river {
    background-color: var(--monokai-bg);
    color: var(--monokai-fg);
}

.tc-theme-pmu-monokai-dark .tc-storyview {
    background-color: var(--monokai-bg);
    color: var(--monokai-fg);
}

.tc-theme-pmu-monokai-dark .tc-tiddler-frame {
    background-color: var(--monokai-bg);
    color: var(--monokai-fg);
}

.tc-theme-pmu-monokai-dark .tc-tiddler-body {
    background-color: var(--monokai-bg);
    color: var(--monokai-fg);
}
```

